          <development character="Kira Voss" tag="trust-built">She deepens her practical engagement and emotional integration with the collective: she proactively suggests running allergy tests concurrently with assessment (agency/decision), calmly submits to novel medical protocols, and reframes the experience—despite bad flavor—as nourishment and part of her new life. This reinforces growing trust and acceptance rather than a abrupt shift.</development>
